source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Mouse control (click, move, down, up)

Usage: bl mouse [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  click  Click at coordinates or current position
  move   Move the mouse to coordinates
  down   Press a mouse button down
  up     Release a mouse button
  help   Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -v, --verbose   Enable debug logging
      --headless  Hide browser window (visible by default)
      --json      Output as JSON
  -h, --help      Print help
